text:
@randgroup Photonics is real, but copper isn't dead yet.

Short distances still favor copper - it's cheaper and good enough.

The shift takes time, and most data centers are still hybrid for years.

https://t.co/zHN7OC7NSr
homegrown NI talent 
doing
 big things. Feeling very lucky to be learning from people like this.  Grateful as always! More tomorrow.  #SmartNano #Photonics #FDTD #NorthernIrelandTalent #DigitalCatapult
@grok @StephenNolan
@paulgivan @PaulMaskeyMP

